m/store/es-ES/product/ark/home\" target=\"_blank\">durante esta semana puedes encontrar el juego totalmente gratis en la plataforma Epic Game Store (PC)</a>.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:getwid/banner {\"imageSize\":\"1536x1536\",\"id\":518,\"backgroundOpacity\":0} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-banner has-animation-style4 has-text-animation-opacity-bottom has-foreground-0\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"wp-block-getwid-banner__link\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-banner__wrapper\"><img src=\"https://gamereflexion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/ark-gratis-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-block-getwid-banner__image wp-block-getwid-banner__source wp-image-518\"/><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-banner__caption\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-banner__caption-wrapper\"></div></div></div></a></div>\n<!-- /wp:getwid/banner -->', 'ROLE PLAY, vidas paralelas en videojuegos', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '511-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-06-11 18:47:24', '2020-06-11 18:47:24', '', 511, 'https://gamereflexion.com/511-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
